                  <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">
                    How do I choose the right type of loan?
                  </summary>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
                    Start with your goal and time horizon. For a home, look at
                    mortgages and HELOCs. For a car, use an auto loan or lease
